SUMMARY:CESE Summer 2026 Jobs & Internships Fair
DESCRIPTION:Come visit the CESE Summer Jobs and Internships Fair! This ev
 ent is for IU students who are interested in connecting with employers of
 fering employment and/or internship opportunities for summer primarily in
  Indiana and the Midwest.  Whether you need to find your summer job OR yo
 u just want to check out all the cool opportunities available to students
  so you can plan ahead for fall\, come on over to Alumni Hall in the Indi
 ana Memorial Union.  Local employers\, non-profits\, and camp programs\, 
 IU departments and on-campus employers\, as well as in-state employer par
 tners will be here to tell you about how you can spend your summer gainin
 g the valuable skills you'll need in whatever career you plan to pursue -
  all while making money and having some fun\, too! You might even be able
  to plan and secure your fall on-campus job NOW - come and see!  Advanced
  registration is not required to participate in this event\, however\, we
  do encourage you to register in advance for the fair so we can let emplo
 yers know you'll be there.Career Exploration &amp\; Student Employment (C
 ESE) is committed to providing access\, equal opportunity and reasonable 
 accommodation for individuals with disabilities in employment\, its servi
 ces\, programs\, and activities. To request reasonable accommodation\, co
 ntact: Angela Martin at aoshepar@iu.edu
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Come visit the CESE Summer Jobs and Int
 ernships Fair! This event is for IU students who are interested in connec
