SUMMARY:Crocs Early Talent Competition: Kick-Off
DESCRIPTION:The Crocs Early Talent Competition is your chance to take on 
 a real-world brand challenge. This is an opportunity to think boldly\, mo
 ve quickly\, and help Crocs with solve a problem.  You'll be able to meet
  Crocs professionals\, add a project to your resume or portfolio\, and be
  entered to win prizes.Join the Kick-off event at 5pm EST to meet the Cro
 cs team and get briefed on the challenge.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><span data-teams="true">The Crocs Early T
 alent Competition is your chance to take on a real-world brand challenge.
  This is an opportunity to think boldly\, move quickly\, and help Crocs w
 ith solve a problem.<br /><br />  You'll be able to meet Crocs profession
 als\, add a project to your resume or portfolio\, and be entered to win p
 rizes.<br /><br /></span><span data-teams="true">Join the Kick-off event 
 at 5pm EST to meet the Crocs team and get briefed on the challenge.</span
 ></p>
