SUMMARY:Research Advancement\, Impact & Leadership
DESCRIPTION:Panelists: George Ball\, Daniel Beneish\, Haizhen Lin\, and D
 on Kuratko  This panel is open to all interested faculty members\, partic
 ularly those who have achieved tenure. It will offer the opportunity to e
 ngage with senior faculty to discuss paths toward advancing your research
  impact and leadership in the field while also navigating service to the 
 school and your discipline. Topics include\, but are not limited to\, hav
 ing an impact on local\, federal\, or international policy\; serving in l
 eadership roles within the field\; becoming Editor-in-Chief\; writing a b
 ook.
