 ment\, and think tanks    </p></li></ul><p data-start="1323" data-end="14
 50"><strong>Lunch will be provided!</strong>&#160\;Come ready to debate\,
  analyze\, and defend your conclusions in an interactive\, off-the-record
  setting.</p>
